text: UMH may refer to: * Miguel Hernández University of Elche, a Spanish university, located in the province of Alicante * Underwood-Memorial Hospital, a hospital in Woodbury, New Jersey, USA * The United Methodist Hymnal * University of Mons-Hainaut, a university in the French Community of Belgium * UMH group, an international multimedia group based in Ukraine
title: UMH
